      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014the paint is sparkling, the interior is flawless, and it drives like an absolute dream. It's been garage-kept and meticulously cared for, so it's basically in perfect shape. I'm sad to let this gem go, but I'm excited for it to find a great new home. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
