    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts a factory-spec Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. The high-revving valvetrain, equipped with dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivers a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically flawless, the chassis integrity has been verified with no subframe fatigue, and the suspension retains its precise factory damping rates. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic with an immaculate Nappa leather interior, this E46 represents the pinnacle of analog driver engagement and remains in pristine, showroom condition.",
