    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule in flawless, showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously climate-controlled and maintained to the highest standards, showing zero signs of wear. The original factory finish boasts a deep, mirror-like luster, entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since new. Every electronic feature and mechanical component functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. The engine bay is detailed to a concours standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. Accompanied by a complete service history from authorized dealerships and all original keys and manuals, this is an investment-grade example for the most discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
